Package gameOfLife

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    App
    The App class represents the application window for Conway's Game of Life.
    Cell
    Represents a Cell in the Grid
    CellAvatar
    The graphical representation of a single Cell.
    Grid
    Represents a grid of Cells that follow the rules of Conway's Game of Life.
    GridRenderer
    A renderer that handles drawing a visual representation (consisting of Black and White 10x10 squares) of a Grid containing Cells that follow the rules of Conway's Game of Life.
    SaveManager
    Save Manager that handles saving/loading the state of the Grid from Conway's Game of Life, writing/reading from .gol (Game Of Life) files.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    CellState
    An Enum class to distinguish between a given cell's state, either DEAD or ALIVE.
